com.guidewire.pl.plugin.document
Interface IDocumentCreationOptions

Deprecated. In the Pebbles world, this interface should no longer be required, since the integration which it makes possible is now directly supported in the .pcf files. 

public interface IDocumentCreationOptions

An optional interface. Implementations providing this interface expose one or more options available for creating documents. These options are typically presented as menu items to the user. They collectively provide a high level menu of choices for initiating the document creation process.
